dji.sdk.api.RemoteController

Class DJIRemoteControllerAttitude

  • java.lang.Object
    • dji.sdk.api.RemoteController.DJIRemoteControllerAttitude

  • public class DJIRemoteControllerAttitude
extends java.lang.Object

    DJI Remote Controller Attitude

    DJI Remote Controller Attitude is designed for receiving the information from pushing packages which are sent by the drone periodically. Here, the data package will be sent from the remote control whenever the value has been changed. For example, the app will receive a data package while the customer is using remote controller to let the drone throttle.
    Version:
    : V2.4.0
    Author:
    : DJI Software
